{"lastModified":1774615784063,"uri":"c::18231584005::vessel::746c0650-f6b7-11f0-8843-711b1e045856","yachtType":["Sailing","Catamaran"],"description":"Operating Area: Greece\n\nThe HeySea 60 represents the pinnacle of modern yacht design, combining Italian craftsmanship with contemporary performance capabilities. This dream yacht stretches approximately 60 feet in length, offering the perfect balance between intimacy and spaciousness for charter guests seeking an unforgettable experience.\n\nBuilt with meticulous attention to detail, Andare Oltre features a sleek flybridge design that maximizes both interior volume and outdoor entertainment areas. The yacht’s hull design ensures exceptional stability and performance, with cruising speeds that allow guests to explore multiple islands during their charter vacation while maintaining supreme comfort.\n\nThe HeySea shipyard has established itself as a leader in the luxury yacht market, particularly in the 50-80 foot segment. Their yachts are renowned for superior build quality, modern aesthetics, and exceptional seaworthiness – qualities that make Andare Oltre a standout choice among charter yachts in Greek waters.\n\nWith a relatively shallow draft, this perfect vessel can access secluded coves and smaller harbors throughout the Greek archipelago that larger yachts simply cannot reach. This accessibility opens up a whole world of hidden gems and pristine beaches that few charter guests ever discover.","blueprint":{"name":"ANDARE OLTRE","images":["/media/media::image::a::vessel::746c0650-f6b7-11f0-8843-711b1e045856::assets::555ca410-f6ba-11f0-9ac7-d3a58ae4ab83/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::746c0650-f6b7-11f0-8843-711b1e045856::assets::54ea8150-f6ba-11f0-9ac7-d3a58ae4ab83/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::746c0650-f6b7-11f0-8843-711b1e045856::assets::554ec160-f6ba-11f0-9ac7-d3a58ae4ab83/{imageVariant}","/media/media::image::a::vessel::746c0650-f6b7-11f0-8843-711b1e045856::assets::55186f20-